subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Janel McCarville scored a career-high 34 points and Lisa Willis added a career-high 19 on Tuesday night to help the Liberty beat the Houston Comets, 90-87, in overtime in a W.N.B.A. game. The Liberty snapped the Comets’ eight-game home winning streak and completed a sweep of their two-game season series.
